{"tid":499201,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU財產小道消息","createTime":"2017-12-14T14:00:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T05:23:07.000Z","uid":34643,"like":14,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"8cc14f5176882f6a789b4dc8281afb41af174e25","tid":499201,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T14:00:49.000Z","msg":"2012年IU身家財產至少100億韓元 現在至少500億韓元以上<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/61ad358bgy1fmgmbx19rbj20ge0f4ab6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F61ad358bgy1fmgmbx19rbj20ge0f4ab6.jpg&h=0521b722&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/61ad358bgy1fmgmby6224j20dr08dt9z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F61ad358bgy1fmgmby6224j20dr08dt9z.jpg&h=a34d7e42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIU父母家是在方背洞 後來在龍山買了30億韓元的住宅 去年搬家到50億韓元的住宅 是跟IU住同個小區的大媽在cafe上透露的<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/61ad358bgy1fmgmc0z8o3j20fb0enaac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F61ad358bgy1fmgmc0z8o3j20fb0enaac.jpg&h=9e15bee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人說IU財產500億 跟公司比例是1:9 IU是9 回復里有人說IU前一次跟經紀公司續約時分成是3:7 IU是7 還有人回復表示在歌謠祭時有人通過工作人員了解到是2:8 IU是8 愛信哪個信哪個。。<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/61ad358bgy1fmgmc35p31j20l60djglr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F61ad358bgy1fmgmc35p31j20l60djglr.jpg&h=631f682b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2015年底IU在雜誌採訪中提到「比現在再多的財產是不必要的」還出過新聞<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/61ad358bgy1fmgmcda71jj20hw0k3t9w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F61ad358bgy1fmgmcda71jj20hw0k3t9w.jpg&h=16625bd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/61ad358bgy1fmgmffrtqoj20bl0dswh3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Fbmiddle%2F61ad358bgy1fmgmffrtqoj20bl0dswh3.jpg&h=ce45a8d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e643dbc8a4f3ed52c8436acfa5f436ba24814e42","tid":499201,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T14:01:17.000Z","msg":"姐係幾錢HKD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a057ab39521c3af16c437abc2b32dafe2f4b863e","tid":499201,"uid":2959,"like":142,"dislike":2,"score":140,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T14:01:45.000Z","msg":"睇錯iu小產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b8d19afd72147e2cd467ee11a14719c905395f","tid":499201,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T14:01:48.000Z","msg":"養我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e953570cd2e0fa55082bc15c0464e854ac57ef87","tid":499201,"uid":4574,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T14:01:58.000Z","msg":"睇錯小產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48413bc46c32bf71307ddccaf1554d5a71f612d3","tid":499201,"uid":33643,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T14:03:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>姐係幾錢HKD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n3億幾4億"},{"pid":"f75291e1df9b90b2f97b3fc70e68c1df0aaa5657","tid":499201,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T14:03:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>姐係幾錢HKD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n3.59億 HKD"},{"pid":"6f7c51098d00db5fb4e8c2cad83c7bc3285a4895","tid":499201,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T14:03:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>姐係幾錢HKD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n3.59億 HKD</blockquote><br />\n就黎比得上穿屎"},{"pid":"390ba7b36e8c44c06b3419cd8d73795687507a86","tid":499201,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T14:09:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><ins><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>IU與東家續約3年免收合約金</strong></div></ins><br />\nLOEN娛樂宣佈與旗下歌手IU續約。<br />\n<br />\nIU與LOEN的合約將於9月到期，而4月雙方就開始就續約等問題討論，本著7年間對彼此的信賴和義氣，IU決定續約3年並不收任何合約金，就此雙方也將攜手走過第一個十年。</blockquote><br />\n師太根本賺到唔洗合約金..."},{"pid":"72c80d404075c4370623953548fe9b6fa12a07df","tid":499201,"uid":65298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T14:16:57.000Z","msg":"g"},{"pid":"3a43907c3cd25fd2030397939ac36168c5d3011d","tid":499201,"uid":34643,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T14:20:27.000Z","msg":"keke<br />\n<img src=\"http://ww4.sinaimg.cn/large/006ajBdMly1fmge07ng85j30tp18gqrl.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fww4.sinaimg.cn%2Flarge%2F006ajBdMly1fmge07ng85j30tp18gqrl.jpg&h=15046e38&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4370e35d0f5b5ab293b7bcfc2fbee911688b68fe","tid":499201,"uid":815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T14:42:00.000Z","msg":"3億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0ad07fc77d5479b75c8d45a20f0022b71f3bf6","tid":499201,"uid":27709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T14:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128f1bb7bc13c0173a4e6f0629e762d22f939e03","tid":499201,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T14:47:55.000Z","msg":"自己作埋歌本應分多幾份啦"},{"pid":"9f658c27ce1509607b68fa4a2e2d2687e0d10440","tid":499201,"uid":43880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-14T15:27:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a931865f926ad7eb4927c8b0f82ba573befbd6","tid":499201,"uid":34643,"like":21,"dislike":0,"scor